{"tid":419550,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一直都好攰？","createTime":"2017-09-30T14:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T04:57:24.000Z","uid":8895,"like":1028,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb7c9070f839d53cc100ffe14ea566798196cd3","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"返工覺得好攰<br />\n收工返到屋企好攰<br />\n去玩又係好攰<br />\n食野又攰<br />\nKeep住都攰既狀態<br />\n做所有事都有心無力 <br />\n攰到好似廢人咁<br />\n廢到連訓教都覺得好攰<br />\n自從返左工就覺得好攰 <br />\n每日就係返工放工訓教<br />\n第二日起身又係咁<br />\n個人無曬動力 好多野都好想做 但覺得攰<br />\n有咩方法可以令自己有返動力 明明以前唔係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7290ac48b57e1c606a8dc2e968aa9a2aa37592","tid":419550,"uid":69522,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:50:00.000Z","msg":"有目標有動力<br />\n沒目標沒動力"},{"pid":"56e1e50819dbdae8b430fe388dc13c2c03cad292","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有目標有動力<br />\n沒目標沒動力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有目標都無動力 對世界都係灰色咁..."},{"pid":"21eaca6fe9ead85387f101751922f9e105df3261","tid":419550,"uid":59886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"Diet"},{"pid":"185bb43475f517d9b0a810affa89552b3c4fef4a","tid":419550,"uid":133,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"我識一個人都係咁"},{"pid":"75de04073b63135f4d3f176c663d44c6b27405d8","tid":419550,"uid":151187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"試下自己一個去下旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f988894d9b185048787f75a2ff5f0192f2cc67","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下自己一個去下旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連自己一個落街跑步做運動既動力都無 旅行更加無 做旅行功課好攰<img src=\"/assets