b0a4a83b8c","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣 仲周身痛</blockquote><br />\n岩岩起身 又覺得攰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edef353e6b9f707015dcb890d987aa497e0e9ec6","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做運動會有d幫助<br />\n但係我最近都好攰。忙到抽吾到時間做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都有咁諗 係咪要返少少運動 例如落街跑個圈 廿分鐘都好 但一諗起攰又係一個藉口 唔想郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7669b8a12b77e291eb79f0f41efef675fd351d77","tid":419550,"uid":143945,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:30:49.000Z","msg":"濕重<br />\n飲土伏苓，少飲汽水，運動"},{"pid":"7674de8c75c5b251b4543b0904ad749ce2fc8b85","tid":419550,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:49:44.000Z","msg":"行屍走肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b730680c18991e2c0866727bdb8732a4c3c7ec","tid":419550,"uid":60291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   明明放假想出去行下但攰攰地 又吽咗係間房一日   愈吽就愈頹愈攰 無限LOOP <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bcb90d05981431e32aceff3addd8f294c6ca30","tid":419550,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"做多d運動..<br />\n會有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b90219e7d01722cea123696d020b1b0bb4bb90","tid":419550,"uid":88875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主一日訓幾個鐘?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  10:30-11:00就會去訓既人</blockquote><br />\n樓主試下訓少一兩個鐘 再用個一兩個鐘黎做運動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a6439570224d46001b16974c186eb05de481d5","tid":419550,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"小弟，有時覺得做人好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64482e3a9c2b8e4262a53e2b26a953c404a0a524","tid":419550,"uid":50162,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"你好大機會有depression了"},{"pid":"df4c9bedd1fb2a6589cf9b30be4d68a2a6a06c21","tid":419550,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"抑鬱 都會有呢種情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做下運動睇下有冇改善先啦"},{"pid":"dd4893f01a7cba04d1a535cd5c14ba909c8fcb32","tid":419550,"uid":126384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:07:49.000Z","msg":"去健身室操完 再食條蕉 包你沒事"},{"pid":"c7e4e2208781ade5868b9e8c7d11bace3a2ce53a","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"聽日去跑下步 如果唔落雨的話 睇下有無改善 <br />\n因為太耐無做過運動 我諗如果跑廿分鐘 已經頂唔順<br />\n都好過無既可？<br />\n主因唔係想減肥 係想自己調整返健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f47201fedda0c8da803bc3fce11dfba58e0a96","tid":419550,"uid":126384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日去跑下步 如果唔落雨的話 睇下有無改善 <br />\n因為太耐無做過運動 我諗如果跑廿分鐘 已經頂唔順<br />\n都好過無既可？<br />\n主因唔係想減肥 係想自己調整返健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己跑唔慣　<br />\n會好辛苦　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為一跑個身就勁撚痕　勁撚乾<br />\n<br />\n我最後去左玩踏步機／太空漫步機／划船機<br />\n爆SEED 玩15分鍾 / 用Tabata 既節奏 <br />\n包你成身汗<br />\n記住做左熱身先<br />\n<br />\n最緊要你搵到岩你既運動<br />\n利申:都係fg, 之排搵緊工都係keep住做運動, 保持鬥志, 宜家同你一樣返緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da806fc85aa394525b1bd900b4d80eba6614453","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽日去跑下步 如果唔落雨的話 睇下有無改善 <br />\n因為太耐無做過運動 我諗如果跑廿分鐘 已經頂唔順<br />\n都好過無既可？<br />\n主因唔係想減肥 係想自己調整返健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己跑唔慣　<br />\n會好辛苦　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為一跑個身就勁撚痕　勁撚乾<br />\n<br />\n我最後去左玩踏步機／太空漫步機／划船機<br />\n爆SEED 玩15分鍾 / 用Tabata 既節奏 <br />\n包你成身汗<br />\n記住做左熱身先<br />\n<br />\n最緊要你搵到岩你既運動<br />\n利申:都係fg, 之排搵緊工都係keep住做運動, 保持鬥志, 宜家同你一樣返緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企無club house 又無做開gym 邊到有得玩器械？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗住都係跑街就算"},{"pid":"fcd4d8758459773c6625dda45f34c42e5b77bb3d","tid":419550,"uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:00:58.000Z","msg":"做咩跟我開埋啲內容完全一樣既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81ffe7bfc4b0df6a9cd6d855dd961b8f4f791d4","tid":419550,"uid":89599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:44:22.000Z","msg":"打得飛機多後遺症😉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4949ebc62526f0effe6400270a243fcea3e175","tid":419550,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:53:29.000Z","msg":"心好累"},{"pid":"ce7e24c78b182f707d110da7b69623a5234be2ef","tid":419550,"uid":132338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:53:52.000Z","msg":"類似樓主ge情況<br />\n之前都同朋友傾過呢個問題<br />\n佢話我未搵到一樣野激起自己動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a02d8f4082e58900ad2d0f3401f364a48cd6968","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩跟我開埋啲內容完全一樣既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來攰既人唔係得自己一個"},{"pid":"44fcbc87267fba19e1cebd0b7d4e7b90dcd72b79","tid":419550,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"係咪番輪班？"},{"pid":"009efccefe3dde08dd54e76b2aefec21ec642991","tid":419550,"uid":92042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:24:09.000Z","msg":"仲以為自己開左post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d24a0be32996443a85a97dcdc5207aa9c5f7c6d","tid":419550,"uid":24642,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"係咪因為返工無滿足感搞到咁<br />\n我有一排就係因為咁搞到成個人頹晒 完全做乜都無心機 日日都強顏歡笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abb50271a83afd5435204806da0a3527d6d634f","tid":419550,"uid":107683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"個post好毒，睇完都覺得好攰⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed05cf2ddf8fe09faa06302275af3c50b272c236","tid":419550,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁 去到邊好累 一起身都好累<br />\n之後發現同情緒病有關 食左血清素好返哂"},{"pid":"52cf2e3fd01ce196010f7552c5e4e9c7d97ca328","tid":419550,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"有冇試過維他命D？<br />\n我少曬太陽同食魚，有段長時間成日覺得好攰，同埋開始有D抑鬱<br />\n中醫話血氣唔夠，食咗藥係好D但唔想長期食中藥，就算食紅棗都唔見有太大改善<br />\n後來睇新聞講缺乏維他命D嘅症狀同自己幾似就試下食<br />\n食完之後好好多<br />\n如果得閒就用薑水加D精油浸下腳都幾好"},{"pid":"5531505cbec07a3514106725af37ecb1c0883cd3","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪因為返工無滿足感搞到咁<br />\n我有一排就係因為咁搞到成個人頹晒 完全做乜都無心機 日日都強顏歡笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n滿足感依樣野...<br />\n我有屋企人講過 我係公司得唔到滿足感 <br />\n即係覺得自己係老闆隻狗 <br />\n我老母話 唔通想日日都有人讚你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗 唔係想日日有人讚 亦唔係想有人讚<br />\n可能係份工唔岩自己 提唔起勁<br />\n得唔到滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a906d28c8ebcde3308b9ba845530dd1e16cff81","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過維他命D？<br />\n我少曬太陽同食魚，有段長時間成日覺得好攰，同埋開始有D抑鬱<br />\n中醫話血氣唔夠，食咗藥係好D但唔想長期食中藥，就算食紅棗都唔見有太大改善<br />\n後來睇新聞講缺乏維他命D嘅症狀同自己幾似就試下食<br />\n食完之後好好多<br />\n如果得閒就用薑水加D精油浸下腳都幾好</blockquote><br />\n無試過 了解下維他命D先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a596b2a348131e604fadc25a430ab7b427390c","tid":419550,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:22:11.000Z","msg":"有冇戒丁？<br />\n我係精神上好辛苦，成日ff自己可以乜到唔洗理"},{"pid":"00d687ed3299d2e2a2c3cc2c2e3f310ac3c9fe09","tid":419550,"uid":141582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"兩個方向<br />\n中醫<br />\n心理醫生"},{"pid":"d28fd31bde9a1c527ffa2d175686f41d3c155905","tid":419550,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪因為返工無滿足感搞到咁<br />\n我有一排就係因為咁搞到成個人頹晒 完全做乜都無心機 日日都強顏歡笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n滿足感依樣野...<br />\n我有屋企人講過 我係公司得唔到滿足感 <br />\n即係覺得自己係老闆隻狗 <br />\n我老母話 唔通想日日都有人讚你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗 唔係想日日有人讚 亦唔係想有人讚<br />\n可能係份工唔岩自己 提唔起勁<br />\n得唔到滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\njob satisfaction 好重要㗎絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得啱，唔係要人讚，得到人哋認同嘅滿足感<br />\n但可以係講緊你做份工慢慢由零學起，慢慢上手，見到自己進步所得嚟嘅滿足感<br />\n或者係同同事相處好好，合作愉快<br />\n當然我唔知你打咩工好難好準確咁就你狀況講啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好搵自己去就份工<br />\n要搵一份可以就到你嘅工<br />\n咁先會有衝勁 唔會攰<br />\n當然要搵咁嘅工喺香港係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗難搵 好多時自己都唔知自己想點<br />\n加油呀絲打 I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e9c439f193928c8d919eb1e4f103d3d97bee0b","tid":419550,"uid":91196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"認真,試下做多d運動,跑下步<br />\n早d訓,夜晚唔好睇咁多手機,個人會精神好多"},{"pid":"803682f197acdfb453a70be1294b6f64665f577e","tid":419550,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9bb51c85fb85ccecf37e726ddb716a5fb027c0d4","tid":419550,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"其實我唔明點解有啲人都係唔做運動 返整工都唔殘<br />\n我返半年無做運動就差咁遠？"},{"pid":"5c2eb313d786cc103baa2dd145d93543a19e3c7e","tid":419550,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"我都係咁"},{"pid":"99d64671aaeb042a931e339bc97206f3db8ec0d7","tid":419550,"uid":124514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最近返工返太多<br />\n又要返學 成個人好攰<br />\n一放假就訓完又訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生就係不停返工返學訓教<br />\n都唔知為乜"},{"pid":"759e1da0524c280fa10dad5589c8d9605fbe70fd","tid":419550,"uid":145631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"日日係屋企無野做就訓 番學番到屋企又訓 人生無乜目標<br />\n目標都係人地對我既期望 咩上大學果類 <br />\n自己就對身邊事物毫無興趣<br />\n分左手就更係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9205959f1b18fadf129887f64929dbb717f3f8","tid":419550,"uid":81559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"仲成日好眼訓<br />\n一唔想做野就訓<br />\n訓醒坐下又訓<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"a32881c14b6b8f976637982174e71a38cba69132","tid":419550,"uid":8895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪因為返工無滿足感搞到咁<br />\n我有一排就係因為咁搞到成個人頹晒 完全做乜都無心機 日日都強顏歡笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n滿足感依樣野...<br />\n我有屋企人講過 我係公司得唔到滿足感 <br />\n即係覺得自己係老闆隻狗 <br />\n我老母話 唔通想日日都有人讚你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗 唔係想日日有人讚 亦唔係想有人讚<br />\n可能係份工唔岩自己 提唔起勁<br />\n得唔到滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\njob satisfaction 好重要㗎絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得啱，唔係要人讚，得到人哋認同嘅滿足感<br />\n但可以係講緊你做份工慢慢由零學起，慢慢上手，見到自己進步所得嚟嘅滿足感<br />\n或者係同同事相處好好，合作愉快<br />\n當然我唔知你打咩工好難好準確咁就你狀況講啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好搵自己去就份工<br />\n要搵一份可以就到你嘅工<br />\n咁先會有衝勁 唔會攰<br />\n當然要搵咁嘅工喺香港係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗難搵 好多時自己都唔知自己想點<br />\n加油呀絲打 I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於有人明白 係睇住自己成長既感足感 <br />\n係依到真係搵唔到樂趣 加投入唔到份工<br />\n公司文化影響 連個人既情緒都影響埋<br />\n團火熄左 就好似依家咁樣<br />\n雖然岩自己既工 真係好重要 <br />\n聽完樓上咁多巴絲打 我應該去做下運動去令自己精神啲<br />\n可能搵到第二份都有機會咁 所以我應該要去搵解決方法<br />\n多謝你既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a9a387342b681109b37575be92ba3f12709656","tid":419550,"uid":24642,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\njob satisfaction 好重要㗎絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得啱，唔係要人讚，得到人哋認同嘅滿足感<br />\n但可以係講緊你做份工慢慢由零學起，慢慢上手，見到自己進步所得嚟嘅滿足感<br />\n或者係同同事相處好好，合作愉快<br />\n當然我唔知你打咩工好難好準確咁就你狀況講啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好搵自己去就份工<br />\n要搵一份可以就到你嘅工<br />\n咁先會有衝勁 唔會攰<br />\n當然要搵咁嘅工喺香港係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗難搵 好多時自己都唔知自己想點<br />\n加油呀絲打 I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於有人明白 係睇住自己成長既感足感 <br />\n係依到真係搵唔到樂趣 加投入唔到份工<br />\n公司文化影響 連個人既情緒都影響埋<br />\n團火熄左 就好似依家咁樣<br />\n雖然岩自己既工 真係好重要 <br />\n聽完樓上咁多巴絲打 我應該去做下運動去令自己精神啲<br />\n可能搵到第二份都有機會咁 所以我應該要去搵解決方法<br />\n多謝你既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做運動可以暫時幫你整到一個目標畀自己，個人無咁迷失<br />\n同埋出一身汗個感覺好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺做完一次運動之後成個人即刻健康咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋你都講好啱，如果唔去搵第二份工嘅，就點都要喺依份工到落手改善，唔好畀自己頹落去<br />\n一係你試下做完一個task 之後，諗諗有冇咩部分係可以下次做好啲，搵本簿記低佢，下次再做嗰陣就改善下<br />\n咁樣可能可以呃到啲滿足感返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司文化幫唔到你，你就靠自己努力啦"},{"pid":"e562860a8db83d492c6c8a47f38f6059869a13b4","tid":419550,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"個人冇目標/負能量就係咁<br />\n我最近一個月開始做運動好咗啲唔係精神攰<br />\n係太熱令我好攰又瞓得差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492d75ba3609a254def3750240c2769cfab0b765","tid":419550,"uid":99691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"自己由中學起都係咁累<br />\n後來發現左自己有mild anxiety<br />\n食左藥 個人精神左好多 <br />\n直程係重生咁"},{"pid":"b4fa1f744baecc0166e3d4525d6bf4e72b06f30c","tid":419550,"uid":70028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"有full time, 一星期再踢5晚足球<br />\n爽啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4a275ea005477ea2a103a04029bec0f077fb69","tid":419550,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f0e8a71cc5153681f42c338fb36eb40b87085e","tid":419550,"uid":67778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"搵個愛你的人，佢就會成為你的目標，可惜香港太難搵，大家愛錢多過愛人"},{"pid":"cc955258bf1b57101591a9a2cf1a757e2378300d","tid":419550,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"A heart that's full up like a landfill<br />\nA job that slowly kills you<br />\nBruises that won't heal<br />\n<br />\nYou look so tired and unhappy<br />\nBring down the government<br />\nThey don't, they don't speak for us<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab770a93d8cb51c8b43f6edb19099b454f9f926","tid":419550,"uid":66679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f01e826e92c6a925cc107c5d6480401d215b31df","tid":419550,"uid":109047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"Same here.<br />\n放工寧願翻屋企 出街就覺好累..<br />\n連出兩晚既話 第2日一定飛機....🤦🏻&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"8ae39967da41f4eeecc73fb9ba370a8becfa8421","tid":419550,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d7e6553aea1ab70e155bb6c0bb921856b5f566","tid":419550,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffb339a7489137b46740eb88f3df0cf7177a4444","tid":419550,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"日日坐係到,屈埋屈埋屈到兩隻腳都有毛病<img src=\"/asse